Raiders Sign Former Giants Tight End Kevin Boss to $16 Million Contract

-- B y   J a y   B e b e r m a n
-- 
2011-08-05T17:59:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/raiders-sign-former-giants-tight-end-kevin-boss-to-16-million-contract.html
The Oakland Raiders signed free-agent
tight end Kevin Boss, the National Football League team said on
its website.  Boss, 27, caught 35 passes for 531 yards and five
touchdowns last season for the  New York Giants .  Terms weren’t disclosed. ESPN reported it’s a four-year
contract worth $16 million.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Jay Beberman at 
 jbeberman@bloomberg.net  